NLP Engineer Roadmap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Natural Language Processing (NLP) Engineering focuses on building systems that understand, interpret, and generate human language. An NLP Engineer works on applications like chatbots, translation systems, sentiment analysis, search engines, and modern large language models.\
This roadmap takes you from programming basics to building advanced NLP systems used in real-world AI products.\
